attributes.Long form description: An instructor helps a man to operate a gopro. Man changes the battery and the SD card. He then turns on the GoPro and turns off the GoPro. Man mounts the GoPro on the strap. He detaches the GoPro from the strap and attaches it to the handheld grip. Man removes the GoPro from the handheld grip and pushes back the mount legs on the GoPro.
